title: Insider Secrets of the Knights Templar
body: Could there be more than one Ark of the Covenant? Current grandmaster of the Knights Templar Timothy Hogan joins host Jimmy Church in this special series opener to explore the mysteries of manna – a physical substance related to ancient alchemical technologies. Revealing how the Knights Templar are in possession of manna and multiple Arks, Hogan fills in the gaps of esoteric history from Egypt to the Bible and today.
teaser: Could there be more than one Ark of the Covenant? Grandmaster of the Knights Templar Timothy Hogan joins host Jimmy Church in this special series opener to explore the alchemical mysteries of manna.

title: Geometric Structures Beyond Duality
body: Are new scientific discoveries linking consciousness and spacetime? Delving into the cosmic connections of consciousness, Superluminal Systems CEO Adam Apollo shares the evolving history of humanity’s understanding of our place in the universe. From the matching geometry of DNA and proton structures to quantum physics rewriting science itself, Apollo pushes us to move beyond duality and resonate within the harmonic universe.
teaser: Are new scientific discoveries linking consciousness and spacetime? Delving into the cosmic connections of consciousness, Superluminal Systems CEO Adam Apollo shares the evolving history of humanity’s understanding of our place in the universe.

title: Human Mothers, Hybrid Children
body: Are women around the world giving birth to hybrid ET children? Clinical hypnotherapist and ET contactee Geraldine Orozco details her personal experiences, as well as what she has learned from her work with women abducted by ETs who have also carried hybrid ET-human babies. As founder of the group Hybrid Mother, Orozco shares support, information, and understanding about the present and future reality of the agendas with hybridization.
teaser: Are women giving birth to hybrid ET children? Clinical hypnotherapist and ET contactee Geraldine Orozco shares her personal experiences, as well as what she has learned from her work with women abducted by ETs who have also carried hybrid ET-human babies.

title: A Harvard Professor’s Search for ET Tech
body:
With the appearance of ‘Oumuamua and other interstellar objects traveling in and out of our solar system, do we finally have proof of non-terrestrial intelligence? Harvard professor and astrophysicist Avi Loeb joins host Jimmy Church to expose the astronomical data, mineral content, and intricate physics behind these interstellar objects and how science is becoming rewritten with the more we discover.

Avi Loeb is author of Extraterrestrial: The First Sign of Intelligent Life Beyond Earth and Professor of Astronomy at Harvard University.
teaser: With the appearance of ‘Oumuamua and interstellar objects traveling in our solar system, do we have proof of non-terrestrial intelligence? Harvard professor and astrophysicist Avi Loeb exposes the data, minerals, and physics behind interstellar objects.

title: A Debrief on UAP Narratives
body: Why has the nomenclature changed from UFOs to UAP (Unidentified Aerial Phenomena) with the regular release of evidence from governments worldwide? Editor-in-chief of The Debrief, Micah Hanks, joins host Jimmy Church to explore the evolution of human understanding and acceptance around non-terrestrial phenomena. From credible scientific data and official reports to the connotations of terminology like UFOs and disclosure, Hanks exposes the intricacies of these world-changing revelations and what they could mean for humanity’s future.
teaser: Why has the nomenclature changed from UFOs to UAP (Unidentified Aerial Phenomena)? Editor-in-chief of The Debrief, Micah Hanks, joins host Jimmy Church to explore the evolution of human understanding and acceptance around non-terrestrial phenomena.

title: Rewriting America’s Origin Story
body: What was a viking runestone doing in North America before the arrival of Christopher Columbus? Forensic geologist Scott Wolter presents his research on the secret history of North America through the 1898 discovery and subsequent examination of a cryptic runestone. Connecting these narratives of the Knights Templar and Founding Fathers, Wolter shares how his research surrounding the contentious Kensington Runestone could rewrite history.
teaser: What was a viking runestone doing in North America before the arrival of Christopher Columbus? Forensic geologist Scott Wolter shares his research on a secret history of America through the 1898 discovery and subsequent examination of a cryptic runestone.

title: The Government’s Reverse-Engineered UFOs
body: Does the leaked Wilson-Davis memo offer substantial evidence of government involvement with extraterrestrials? UFO investigative researcher Melinda Leslie joins Jimmy Church to analyze top-secret notes on a meeting between Admiral Thomas Wilson and astrophysicist Dr. Eric Davis. Evidence shows the government has funded the reverse engineering of ET craft by private aerospace contractors, and exposed how UAP technology has become a corporate secret over time.
teaser: Does the leaked Wilson-Davis memo offer substantial evidence of government involvement with extraterrestrials? UFO investigative researcher Melinda Leslie analyzes top-secret notes on a meeting between Admiral Thomas Wilson and astrophysicist Eric Davis.

title: UFO Crash at Nuclear Test Site
body:
How is the Trinity crash of 1945 in New Mexico related to the Manhattan Project and nuclear test sites? New witnesses are coming forward with testimony about the crash of a non-terrestrial craft following the infamous Trinity nuclear bomb tests. Legendary UFO researcher Jacques Vallée, Ph.D., details the history of this crash retrieval, which was secretly removed from New Mexico during a 10-day operation. Analyzing evidence of terrain damage and Army involvement, Vallée explores the connections of nuclear explosions with UAP.

Jacques Vallée, Ph.D., is a computer and AI scientist whose work inspired Close Encounters of the Third Kind. Vallée and Paola Harris co-authored the book TRINITY: The Best Kept Secret.
teaser: How is the Trinity crash of 1945 related to the Manhattan Project and nuclear test sites? Legendary UFO researcher Jacques Vallée, Ph.D., details the history of this crash retrieval, which was secretly removed from New Mexico during a 10-day operation.

title: Ancient Cataclysms That Reset Humanity
body: How many times have advanced human civilizations been wiped clean by catastrophic events? Celebrated author Randall Carlson joins Jimmy Church to offer insight on a wide variety of topics relating to an event or series of catastrophes that wiped our Earth clean of ancient history. Challenging narratives of academically-accepted archeology by citing new evidence and data points, Carlson is dedicated to finding and sharing the truth about Earth’s evolution and the possibility of a future cataclysm to come.
teaser: How many times have advanced human civilizations been wiped clean by catastrophic events? Celebrated author Randall Carlson joins Jimmy Church to offer insight on topics relating to catastrophes that wiped our Earth clean of ancient history.

title: Living Architecture of Ancient Egypt
body: Is the megalithic architecture of Egypt alive and able to function as energy technology? Offering first-hand experience from their joint explorations throughout Egypt, author Billy Carson joins host Jimmy Church to unravel the mysteries of ancient, advanced engineering at different sites. From rarely-accessed locations like tunnels below the Sphinx in Giza to subterranean aqueous temple sites like Dendera, Carson and Church share their mystical experiences and what new discoveries could mean for our past and future.
teaser: Is the megalithic architecture of Egypt alive? Offering first-hand experience from their joint explorations throughout Egypt, author Billy Carson joins host Jimmy Church to unravel the mysteries of ancient, advanced engineering at different sites.

title: Discovering Exoplanets & ET Life
body: Could humanity be on the edge of discovering intelligent life on exoplanets in nearby galaxies? As the James Webb Space Telescope delivers paradigm-shifting images from beyond our solar system, experts like futurist and author John Michael Godier are exploring the mounting evidence and statistical likelihood that humanity is not alone in the universe. Sharing data from his research, Godier offers insight on the untapped potential of exoplanets, the visible melding of multiple galaxies, and the oldest solar systems that could contain unfathomable secrets.
teaser: Could humanity soon discover intelligent life on exoplanets in nearby galaxies? Sharing data from the James Webb Space Telescope, John Michael Godier explores exoplanets, the melding of galaxies, and the oldest star systems with unfathomable secrets.

title: Journalist Exposes US-ET Intel
body: What evidence do we have of extraterrestrial phenomena on Earth? Concluding season one of Into the Vortex, award-winning journalist Linda Moulton Howe shares her decades of research and direct experience with whistleblowers revealing US government involvement with ETs and UAP. With the mission of informing humanity of truths kept too long in the shadows, Howe relays insider intel, data, and experiences to demonstrate the mounting proof we are not alone.
teaser: What evidence do we have of ETs and UAP on Earth? Concluding season one of Into the Vortex, award-winning journalist Linda Moulton Howe shares her decades of research and experience with whistleblowers revealing US government involvement with ETs and UAP.

title: Black Ops Whistleblower
body: Is there a mysterious “Black Team” responsible for retrieving non-human biologics and unidentified craft shot down by military organizations? Appearing for the first time on Gaia with a new level of disclosure, former Marine and courageous whistleblower, Mike Herrera, sheds light on persistent covert programs and the possession of reverse-engineered ET technology. Despite the potentially dark implications of his revelations, Herrera envisions a future where humans can interface with off-world technology and expand consciousness to change life on Earth for the better.
teaser: Is a mysterious “Black Team” retrieving non-human biologics and unidentified craft?

title: DC Legislates Disclosure
body: Will the American government finally unveil the truth about non-human species with advanced technology? Daniel Sheehan, a prominent justice attorney and founder of the Christic Institute, is at the forefront of this quest for transparency. Armed with a strategic legal approach and the power of subpoenas, he is determined to expose humanity's secret interactions with extraterrestrial civilizations, anticipating a revelation that could change our understanding of the universe forever.
teaser: Will the American government unveil the truth about non-humans with advanced tech?

title: Training for Light System Initiation
body:
Are there other planets with societies that do not experience war, and is that a possibility for our collective future? 

Host Jimmy Church is joined by UNIFYD World founder Jason Shurka to investigate this and other vast questions of universal consciousness. In 2020, Shurka was selected by an undercover organization, The Light System, to release a document known as The Pyramid Code. As a spokesperson in training for TLS, Shurka reveals his thoughts on whether evil is a choice, how suppression of information keeps us divided, and if the silver lining of human hardship is spiritual ascension. Hear Shurka’s insights into the Great Pyramid’s link to mystical Judaism as well as his perspective on what happens to collective consciousness when humanity numbs itself to pain occurring across the world.
teaser: Are there other planets that don't experience war, and is that our future?

title: Jimmy Church's Cosmic Hypnotic Regression
body: Join host Jimmy Church for his first-ever hypnosis regression session with acclaimed hypnotherapist Sarah Breskman Cosme as she unlocks his hidden memories of ET contact. Witness the real-time reactions of both Church and Breskman Cosme to his subconscious revelations as a “pioneer of disclosure.” As Church reflects with gratitude upon his life path, he ponders possible implications of hypnotic regression on his own mission as well as for our collective.
teaser: Join Jimmy Church for his first-ever session with hypnotherapist Sarah Breskman Cosme.

title: Quantum Codes, Creation & Consciousness
body:
Are all human beings made of particles within an infinite field of quantum creation, holding vibrational codes similar to technology’s 1’s and 0’s?
 
Host Jimmy Church embarks on a deeply intriguing conversation with Matthew James Bailey, known for pioneering advances into the ethical use of AI, to explore the scientific evidence which quantifies universal consciousness. From the Source Stargate to energetic entanglement, Bailey suggests each individual holds the potential to use data for measurement, validation, and improvement. Is the universe ultimately inviting us to apply internal codes of creation for collective awakening and transformation?
teaser: Are all human beings made of particles within an infinite field of quantum creation?

title: Unexplained Orbs: ET or Religious Origin?
body: On a 2007 family fishing trip, author Chris Bledsoe was initiated into a series of contact experiences with ET phenomena. Bledsoe recounts multiple close encounters with energy orbs, including an entity he calls The Lady. In his book, “UFO of God,” Bledsoe draws parallels to the Vatican’s Miracle of the Sun and shares the positive impact of his family’s ET contact on government agencies and religious institutions.
teaser: Chris Bledsoe recounts close encounters with energy orbs and an entity, The Lady.

title: 9D Pleiadian Collective: Disclosure Timeline
body: The 9th Dimensional Pleiadian Collective, keepers of timelines and records, forecasts deadlines for public disclosure. Channel Wendy Kennedy answers questions of ET contact and global disclosure on behalf of light beings located in the constellation called the Seven Sisters. She offers new insights into frequency wars or the battle for humanity’s energy, and discusses how all humans have the ability to channel any form of creative expression.
teaser: The 9th Dimensional Pleiadian Collective forecasts deadlines for public disclosure.

title: Arks, Artifacts & Knights Templar
body:
Did the Knights Templar relocate biblical artifacts from the Holy Land and was the secret order aware of the whereabouts of the legendary Ark of the Covenant?
 
Andrew Gough, historic investigator, and host Jimmy Church explore the secrets of the Temple of Solomon's treasures and the enduring legacy of the Knights Templar. Gough illuminates the spiritual and geographical journey of the chest made famous in Hollywood blockbuster films. He also discusses other sacred relics sacked by religious raiders or stored by Templars for safekeeping. Excavations by Gough’s team have revealed underground chambers and protected sites that are validated by psychic and technological methods.
teaser: Were the Knights Templar aware of the whereabouts of the Ark of the Covenant?

title: Disclosure Delay & Agency Competition
body: Richard Doty, retired AFOSI officer, joins Jimmy Church with an update on congressional whistleblower testimony and insight on the competition between three-letter agencies for control of UAP disclosure. Doty’s direct experiences at Area 51 and inside knowledge of what transpired after Project Blue Book allegedly closed gives new context to the potential location of creature-containment facilities. Also, see photographs from the crash site where an F-22 was ordered to shoot down an unidentified craft.
teaser: Get insight on three-letter agency competition for control of UAP disclosure.

title: UAPs Piloted by Consciousness
body:
Can psychic women pilot an ET craft by becoming one with the ship?

Grant Cameron, author and award-winning international researcher, talks openly about his interviews with sky pilots who control UAPs with consciousness. Cameron’s research suggests that experiencers fly these ships — without controls or a power supply. Using humans with the gift of remote viewing as a conscious interface has been approved by the Department of Defense, according to Cameron. 

What evidence from the 2002 Wilson-Davis document and recent Congressional testimony from Retired Maj. David Grusch corroborates witness reports of 36 sky pilots — most of whom are women? And from Disney to NASA, is DOBSER material designed to force public disclosure?
teaser: Can psychic women pilot an ET craft by becoming one with the ship?
